indicated as accurate per Jump for J-2 or 3 vessels. Seeings as that\'s
potentially (14 KL @ 3t/KL = ~40 tonnes, of ore, for example) from
door to door, virtually (e.g., pithead to smelter), it seems to be pretty
cheap too.

        Yours truly,
                Steven Hudson
