    'topic' => 'Hiver language translation (and grav belt controls)',
    'body' => 'Sat, 11 Apr 1998 17:17:21 -0400  "Chris Seamans" <semo@pil.net> wrote:

>>   IIRC, CT Hivers required keyboard/screen combos to convert
>> their finger wriggling language to spoken commo.
